videos.description: Matt Farrell drives down the baseline and lays it in for Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Farrell makes nice reverse layup for the Irish

videos.description: Nikola Djogo sets up Martinas Geben under the basket and he finishes with a slam for the Irish.
videos.headline: Geben pumps up crowd with slam dunk
